      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/apollo-s-asia-expansion-has-lured-in-35-billion-from-region</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司 (Apollo Global Management Inc.) 对其亚洲业务的改造已开始取得成效：自 2022 年初以来，该公司已从该地区筹集了 350 亿美元资金以支持扩张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/apollo-s-asia-expansion-has-lured-in-35-billion-from-region</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
